<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kipaka van gam zuonten lasau, hun sawt mahleh,
 Ginna'n la ngaihnawp um san chunglam a khun ka um;
 Ngaiin, vangsakna tangah, tang lopi-ah ka ding,
 Jordan gal chuh ka etin, Lalpa gamtiem ka mui.

[V2]
 La ngaihnawpum sa zel un,
 La chuh na sak cheng un;
 Ka lung kipahna'n a dim,
 Ka pak seng puoi, Lalpa!

[V3]
 2. Sau un, lawpa Van zuonte, leia I um lai un,
 Van la leh Isu I nicheng kipahnau hi hen;
 Thusim lui chuh lan sai tiu, ei tatdawkna la chuh,
 Kumsawt lapawl chuh ahi, van gam chana ding chuh.

[V4]
 3. Sau-un lawpa van zuonte'n, a phat sawt ta puona,
 Pathien gam nuom tun chanin van la go chuh sai tiu;
 Guol deihte'n ei ngak zing ui luipang lehlam a khun,
 Luigal achun tuok hitiu, tui kinawk beihna ah.</lyrics>
<title>SING ON</title>
</song>